♪Ang malamig mong tono♪

00:26:59.038 --> 00:27:02.163
♪Mga sugat sa buong buhay♪

00:27:02.782 --> 00:27:05.352
♪Ang pinakamapait na mantsa ng luha♪

00:27:05.352 --> 00:27:09.150
♪Paso ang aking labi♪

